{"id":172,"date":"2017-11-02T07:02:02","date_gmt":"2017-11-02T07:02:02","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/tour.khowebseotop.vn\/?p=172"},"modified":"2017-11-02T07:02:02","modified_gmt":"2017-11-02T07:02:02","slug":"kinh-nghiem-checking-da-lat-mua-dong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/dulich1.webtudong8giay.com\/kinh-nghiem-checking-da-lat-mua-dong\/","title":{"rendered":"Kinh nghi\u1ec7m checking \u0110\u00e0 L\u1ea1t m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>S\u00e0 b\u00e0i \u0111i!!! Vi\u1ec7t Anh v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac chuy\u1ebfn\u00a0du l\u1ecbch L\u00e0o t\u1ef1 t\u00fac\u00a0trong 10 ng\u00e0y, v\u00e0 gi\u1edd m\u00ecnh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u1eb9p trong chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i lang thang d\u1ecdc v\u00f9ng B\u1eafc L\u00e0o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p>N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 L\u00e0o, m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd v\u00ed v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a L\u00e0o v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00f4 g\u00e1i v\u00f9ng s\u01a1n c\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00f4 g\u00e1i \u1ea5y h\u1ed3n nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft xanh trong m\u00e0u ng\u1ecdc b\u00edch, \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng th\u00e1c trong r\u1eebng s\u00e2u. C\u00f2n m\u00e1i t\u00f3c n\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i nh\u01b0 d\u00f2ng Mekong t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ph\u01b0\u01a1ng B\u1eafc.<\/p>\n<p>N\u00e0ng gi\u1ea5u k\u00edn n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau nh\u1eefng r\u1eebng c\u00e2y xanh b\u1ea1t ng\u00e0n n\u00ean n\u00e0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea5y b\u00ed \u1ea9n, m\u1edbi m\u1ebb, l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng\u00a0 k\u1ebb y\u00eau th\u00edch kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1. Hi\u1ec1n h\u00f2a, gi\u1ea3n d\u1ecb, l\u1eb7ng l\u1ebd, y\u00ean b\u00ecnh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Vi\u1ec7t Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 L\u00e0o.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4081\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4081 lazyloaded\" src=\"http:\/\/tour.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/xin-chao-161.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 999px) 100vw, 999px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/tour.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/xin-chao-161.jpg 999w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-luang-prabang-2-300x199.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-luang-prabang-2-768x509.jpg 768w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-luang-prabang-2-696x461.jpg 696w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-luang-prabang-2-634x420.jpg 634w\" alt=\"kinh nghi\u1ec7m du l\u1ecbch Luang Prabang\" width=\"999\" height=\"662\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/tour.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/xin-chao-161.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"http:\/\/tour.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/xin-chao-161.jpg 999w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-luang-prabang-2-300x199.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-luang-prabang-2-768x509.jpg 768w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-luang-prabang-2-696x461.jpg 696w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/kinh-nghiem-du-lich-luang-prabang-2-634x420.jpg 634w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 999px) 100vw, 999px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u00e1c Koung Si \u1edf Luang Prabang<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 L\u00e0o trong tr\u00e1i tim m\u00ecnh. C\u00f2n nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi\u00a0<strong>Luang Prabang<\/strong>, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0a b\u1ea1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh y\u00ean \u2013 tr\u00e1i tim c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 g\u00e1i. L\u00e0 kinh \u0111\u00f4 ho\u00e0ng gia c\u1ee7a v\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u1ed1c L\u1ea1n X\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y g\u1ea7n 7 th\u1ebf k\u1ef7. L\u00e0 n\u01a1i g\u1ee3i nh\u1eafc cho du kh\u00e1ch v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng con ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5, n\u01a1i b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n \u0111o\u00e0n s\u01b0 kh\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i qua, l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 nh\u1ecf nh\u1eafn xinh x\u1eafn mang \u0111\u1eadm d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac Ph\u00e1p \u1edf ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5, du kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 ng\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 \u0111ang l\u1ea1c v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1eddi \u00c2u \u1edf gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ea5t \u00c1. V\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i ho\u00e0ng h\u00f4n tr\u00ean ng\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed3i cao nh\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1, ng\u1eafm nh\u00ecn m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi l\u1eb7n, c\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4 l\u00ean \u0111\u00e8n. C\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i ch\u00f9a c\u1ed5 v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch trang tr\u00ed \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y \u1edf\u00a0<strong>Luang Prabang<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0i d\u00f2ng, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a b\u1ea1n \u0111i\u00a0<strong>du l\u1ecbch Luang Prabang L\u00e0o<\/strong>\u00a0m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<div id=\"toc_container\" class=\"no_bullets contracted\">\n<p class=\"toc_title\">Luang Prabang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><strong>Luang Prabang<\/strong>\u00a0l\u00e0 t\u00ean g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a kinh \u0111\u00f4 c\u0169, n\u01a1i khai sinh ra v\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u1ed1c L\u1ea1n X\u1ea1n (hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Tri\u1ec7u Voi).\u00a0L\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a ph\u00eda B\u1eafc L\u00e0o, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kinh \u0111\u00f4 ho\u00e0ng gia tuy nhi\u00ean di\u1ec7n t\u00edch v\u00e0 m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e2n s\u1ed1 \u1edf Luang Prabang nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 th\u01b0a (ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi 22,000 ng\u01b0\u1eddi). B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nghe th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 xe. S\u1ebd th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 d\u1ec5 th\u1edf v\u00e0 tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb v\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eaft v\u00ec ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac quy ho\u1ea1ch \u1edf Luang Prabang l\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n n\u00e9t x\u01b0a c\u0169 (kh\u00f4ng cho x\u00e2y nh\u00e0 qu\u00e1 2 t\u1ea7ng).<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4097\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4097 lazyloaded\" src=\"http:\/\/tour.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/xin-chao-161-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/tour.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/xin-chao-161-1.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/DSC_8883-300x182.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/DSC_8883-768x466.jpg 768w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/DSC_8883-696x422.jpg 696w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/DSC_8883-692x420.jpg 692w\" alt=\"kinh nghi\u1ec7m du l\u1ecbch luang prabang\" width=\"1000\" height=\"607\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/tour.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/xin-chao-161-1.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"http:\/\/tour.khowebseotop.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/xin-chao-161-1.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/DSC_8883-300x182.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/DSC_8883-768x466.jpg 768w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/DSC_8883-696x422.jpg 696w, https:\/\/dulichbui24.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/DSC_8883-692x420.jpg 692w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 b\u00ecnh y\u00ean \u1edf Luang Prabang<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>M\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Luang Prabang \u0111ang n\u1eb1m g\u1ecdn trong v\u00f2ng tay c\u1ee7a d\u00f2ng Mekong, mang theo bao ph\u00f9 sa \u0111\u1eafp b\u1ed3i t\u1eeb r\u1eebng gi\u00e0 ph\u00eda B\u1eafc. N\u1eb1m trong s\u1ef1 che ch\u1edf c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng n\u00fai, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3i. Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 du l\u1ecbch xanh \u2013 y\u00ean b\u00ecnh \u2013 ch\u01b0a th\u1ea5y \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u \u201cr\u1ea5t L\u00e0o\u201d \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf!<\/p>\n<h2><span id=\"minh-thich-gi-nhat-o-luang-prabang\">M\u00ecnh th\u00edch g\u00ec nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Luang Prabang?<\/span><\/h2>\n<p>N\u1ebfu h\u1ecfi th\u00edch g\u00ec nh\u1ea5t? Ch\u1eafc m\u00ecnh th\u00edch m\u00e0u xanh, xanh c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng r\u1eebng c\u00e2y, c\u1ee7a n\u00fai \u0111\u1ed3i, c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng th\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc, con s\u00f4ng, hay \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u00e2m h\u1ed3n con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Ai \u0111\u1ebfn Luang Prabang r\u1ed3i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd xanh, c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn k\u00ec l\u1ea1!<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n th\u00edch m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u1eefa, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u00e0u xanh, l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng trang tr\u1ea1i voi c\u00f3 c\u00e1c thu\u1ea7n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Voi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n g\u1eady nh\u1ecdn hay roi da. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa voi b\u1eb1ng gi\u1ecdng n\u00f3i \u2013 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u1ea5y khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 du kh\u00e1ch n\u00e0o c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean, tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ed3 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9. N\u01a1i duy nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean c\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ch\u00fa voi, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4084\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=